# Ignore everything ...
*
**/*

# ... except subdirectories containing a .gitignore ...
# NOTE: This causes a scan of all subdirectories, looking for .gitignore files.
#   To prevent scans of huge/slow directories add a .gitignore to explicitly
#   ignore all subdirectories, as in:
#     ./Library/CloudStorage/.gitignore
!**/
!**/.gitignore
tmp/**/
trash/**/

# these have to be explicitly ignored because they sometimes contain git repos
.cargo/
.cache/
.opam/
.git/
.local/share/pnpm
.goenv/
.zkbd/

# dontcare:
.fzf/

# binaries and local files
.vscode
.aider*
.env

# test/check harness (../.claude/todo.kb/2026-07-08-000-Reunify-dotfiles.kb/
# 2026-07-07-000-CI-and-testing-foundations.md); narrow opt-in landed ahead of
# the rest of this file's reconciliation, which is still task 004's -- see
# that task file's Notes for why splitting this slice out was safe.
!test.do
!default.tested.do
!default.checked.do
!HACKING.md
